Description: Quick command launcher with web search and AI chat
 Launcher is a lightweight, Spotlight-style command bar with web search,
 an embedded browser, and multi-provider AI chat (OpenAI, Claude, Kimi,
 OpenRouter, and any OpenAI-compatible endpoint).
 .
 It is frameless, always-on-top, and keyboard-driven, and saves your AI
 conversation history in a lateral panel.
